breakingChangesNotes:
• The ctix-delete-tag command has been removed. Any Playbooks or Automations using this command may break and need to be updated.
  • The ctix-get-indicator-relations command has been renamed to ctix-get-object-relations. Any Playbooks or Automations using this command may break and need to be updated.
  • The query argument has been removed from the ctix-saved-result-set command. Playbooks or Automations using this argument may break and need to be updated.
Make sure to check and update any Playbooks/Scripts that use the above commands or arguments.
